    <note>Cai(1) Ting [1661] Kang's [1653] younger brother, Zheng's [3856] cousin, Meng's [1654], Tianshen's [1660] father, and Tianqiu's [7069] uncle. Wang(2) Huan's and then his younger brother, Yan(6)'s, son-in-law. Huan [3957] and Yan(6) [3992] were brothers of Wang(2) Yaochen's [1919] father, Du [3986]. The father-in-law of Ting's son, Yi [3859], was Guo(1) Shenxi [956]. His son Xiu's [3858] wife was Zhang(1) Fangping's [217] sister. His son, Gu [3862], was Fan(2) Chunren's [559] son-in-law and Wang(2) Zhi(2) [7079] was his maternal grandfather. Zhang Fangping, WJ, 40.33b-46a; Zhu Changwen, WJ, 10.10a-15a (wife #1, born Wang, who died in 1038 at age 26); XCB, 181.14a-14b, 182.15b, 196.4b (n.); XCBSB, 4.16a, 5.25a; Bi Zhongyou, WJ, 14.8a; SHY:ZG, 65.14b; SS, 328.14b. CBD, 5, 3790-1.</note>
